t: "O towniri maw…ìe makko …ìen …ói…óo ka belorki(danki), …ìe naayirani mo sujjugol. O maaki:\"Ko onon yo baaba'en, ko …óum …óoo woni firo koy…óol am ngol oya tuma, gom…óii Joomi am wa…óii ngol goonga. Gom…óii O mo∆¥∆¥ike e am tuma O yaltinnoo lam ka kaso, O itti on ka ladde, …ìaawo nde seytaane bonnii hakkunde am e ben-gootoo…ìe am …ìen. Pellet, Joomi am ko newanii…óo ko O muuyi kon. Ko Kanko woni Anndu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"